Content:
Hello World.<p>A close friend and I have been collaborating for a few years now and we couldn't find a very good simple collaborative to-do app.<p>So we made our own.<p>We'd love any feedback you're willing to provide. It's all free and we plan on keeping it that way. Create an account test it out and give it to us straight.<p>You can also submit feedback through the site as well.<p>Thanks,<p>Ethan Hackett 
@EthanHackett
@AndFinished
